        Yes, EX is a perfectly valid Scrabble word worth 9 points in both TWL and SOWPODS dictionaries. It means a former partner (noun) or the letter X. What makes EX truly powerful isn't just its score — it's the sheer number of hook words available. SEX, HEX, VEX, DEX, REX, LEX, and more all build from EX, making it one of the most versatile 2-letter plays in the game.
      </p>

